rComments: Best Professor i've had at the U of O. Makes philosophy interesting and makes you want to actually go to class, gives out easy assignments and also gives out bonus percentages just for being present. Great Professor.

Hands down the best decision/course I've taken as a student thus far. The course itself is honestly an easy A. The Professor made the class very interesting, he's simply a beauty in my books. I rarely read the book, class is honestly 90% group discussion. I highly recommend this course as well as the Professor.

PHI1102. He's pretty easygoing and almost nothing is covered in class so you have to teach yourself. The exams are extremely specific, arbitrary, and are mostly on stuff not covered in class. Your grade depends on the TA you get. Mine was Lucas Jurkovic and he wrote disgustingly biased and unprofessional comments on my paper.  If you get him, run.
